For example, Code in javascript can accept a function or a string, but in shell it only accepts a string.

Javascript --> Shell:

{code:javascript}
Code(function(x){console.log(x)};) --> Code("function(x){console.log(x)};")
{code}
Shell --> Javascript 
{code:javascript}
